==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Looping
<hw>Loop"ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. D. <ets>loopen</ets> to run.
Cf. <er>Loop</er> a mass of iron, <er>Leap</er>.]</ety>
<fld>(Metal.)</fld> <def>The running together of the matter of an ore
into a mass, when the ore is only heated for calcination.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Looping</ent>⟦br⟧

