<p><cs><col><b>Looping snail</b></col> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>, <cd>any
species of land snail of the genus <gen>Truncatella</gen>; -- so called
because it creeps like the measuring worms.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

